  <p>Clears all the auxiliary buffers identified in the <code>buffers</code> mask, and if
that includes the color buffer then the specified @color is used.</p>
  <p>Since 1.8</p>
<terms>
<item>
<title><code>buffers</code></title>
  <p>A mask of <link xref="Cogl.BufferBit"/>&lt;!-- --&gt;'s identifying which auxiliary
  buffers to clear</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>red</code></title>
  <p>The red component of color to clear the color buffer too if
      specified in <code>buffers</code>.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>green</code></title>
